html:
Nysa Star Żuk Jelcz
The old man rode FSO
As long as possible
Had four part stores
Rusty wrecks is all now
Ruins of old civilization
Forgotten by the old
Not known by the new
An unknown community
Of dead legends
Flooded by rains
Eaten by corrosion
The battle is over now
The dusts fell on the ground
I wish we’ll meet
On road to Starachowice
title: Road
